  <brief_title>A Phase I Study in Healthy Volunteers to Assess Safety of BMS747158</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Single-Dose, Phase I, Dosimetry, Biodistribution, and Safety Trial of BMS 747158 in Healthy Subjects</official_title>
